Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是母亲的资料文件而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是最新世代的NEO-GIN的母体遗传基因提供者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是玛丽亚的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 兑现了承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来检查一下现在装备了CloneBlade的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你很期待哦 玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是最完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能在一起呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩溃在继续着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也确认了精神状态产生混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有预想中的深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许和之前崩溃的志织一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说这就是这次想要确认的所谓母亲的感情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是咖啡奶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好安静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是我父亲建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是在安慰我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不说的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算联络上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之　你马上去接梨穗子回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NswF的那些姐妹不单只是由被选择的遗传基因出生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们自己也被作为母体提供遗传基因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是闻所未闻的近亲交配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近亲? 什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 所有姐妹的父亲的遗传基因都是一个人提供的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进而 下个世代的姐妹们也是用相同的父亲的遗传基因 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于那个男人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些姐妹即是女儿也是妻子 还是孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我猜测 那个父亲就是教父 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这么做我是不知道 但一定不是些什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管离NswF有多远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稣峰玲奈也是姐妹中的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那家伙不是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把梨穗子带回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她和那种怪物在一起的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正·胸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:05:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有要回来的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么资格啊 明明那么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说Lady是怪物 要我把梨穗子接回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有资格这么说人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady救过梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有钱 又是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说 她是真正的妈妈呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我来 她才能让梨穗子更加幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的这么想的话 就没有必要再烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃早饭了哦 玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天西田先生有公事外出 今天就休息一天好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要出去买东西的话派车送你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了我在房间玩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就老老实实的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是玛丽亚的妈妈 一定要玛丽亚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拷贝个人资料是禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是做个笔记而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能给外人看的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张两人幽会的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你老婆看看会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天好像身体不太好的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blade的版本也不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陌生的面孔 也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是次世代的NEO-GIN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女儿 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是玛丽亚的妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道她的来历
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料中的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就是 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是玛丽亚的姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这么矮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是自然分娩的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料记录她已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是旧的纪录 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者 是故意篡改的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情随便它好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去停车场在汽车里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下 坐下来慢慢说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去买东西  能在这里等一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 全部都是玛丽亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是骗人的 都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不可能会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  玛丽亚在训练还有学习都很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈是玛丽亚的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不是和玛丽亚在一起呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么多抱抱玛丽亚呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 有着惊人的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是X-CON? 还是NEO-GIN?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 是在远处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有着很强的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 走回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败她的可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要多问 待在这里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我会回来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才看上去稍微有点妈妈的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二世代NEO-GIN的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定把梨穗子带到别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我会回来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种没有根据的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是那么回事 遗传基因信息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在那边 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让她消失 让开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈讨厌玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我的妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也给我…消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了 受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泽为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到了 梨穗子有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有妈妈的资格哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 不要躲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让我打中 玛丽亚要生气了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 真让人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有很香味道 但是去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泽 那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也许不知道 但是这种怪物是存在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你们碰那孩子一根手指!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 已经不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来得让那个消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不能理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不是我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱用自己的力量是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不弄清楚的话没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 立刻回收
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没这个必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你的妈妈正赶过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败那些怪物 是你妈妈的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妈妈不回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为妈妈已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那个家伙是为了谁在做这么危险的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 全都是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙一直都只是为了你而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她最喜欢梨穗子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:18:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 有受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玲奈吗 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的回收班已经在赶过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈 把那孩子交回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 研究已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我第一次在战斗中感受到了快感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为崩溃还是因为要保护那个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在研究着自己 结果…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还是不能理解 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在以前 只是在一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你也产生了不能理解的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在那一瞬间…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长先生说要带我们去海边玩  
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 目的虽然有的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说斗泽的朋友的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比梨穗子稍微大一点孩子也会去 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人期待  
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一直也没有带你去哪里玩玩
